  "title": "Cost Accountant (Manufacturing/ SAP/ East Region)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Handle SAP month-end closing activities.</li><li>Run monthly/quarterly product costing in SAP.</li><li>Coordinate and prepare budget planning with all departments.</li><li>Monitor and control manufacturing costs.</li><li>Manage inventory for Finished Goods, spare parts, consumables, and WIP.</li><li>Support monthly management reporting.</li><li>Prepare cost control reports and analysis.</li><li>Assist in audit schedule preparation.</li><li>Support ad-hoc financial and business projects.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Accountancy or related field.</li><li>Minimum 5 years’ experience, ideally in manufacturing.</li><li>Proficient in SAP (mandatory).</li><li>Strong skills in Microsoft Excel and PowerPoint.</li></ul><p><strong>______________________________________________________</strong></p><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY :</strong></p><p><strong>Interested candidates, please submit your resume by clicking on “Quick Apply” or contact win@hkmsvs.com for more details.</strong></p><p><strong>Please provide following information in the resume for immediate processing</strong></p><p><strong>1) Reasons for leaving current and/or last employment</strong></p><p><strong>2) Last drawn and/or current salary</strong></p><p><strong>3) Expected salary</strong></p><p><strong>4) Date of availability and/or Notice Period</strong></p><p><strong>All applications will be treated in strictest confidence and only shortlisted candidates will be notified</strong></p><p><strong>Wee Wai Dan</strong></p><p><strong>EA License No : 03C5391</strong></p><p><strong>EA Reg No : R22109628</strong></p>",
